Shanelle Workman https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Shanelle_Workman 0 Shanelle Workman is an American actress, voice actress, producer and director. She is best known for playing the roles of Sarah "Flash" Roberts on the ABC soap opera One Life to Live and Gabriela 'Gaby' Moreno Forester on the CBS soap opera The Bold and the Beautiful.
